mediauploader:
{{doc-special|MediaUploader}}
MediaUploader is a wizard to upload multimedia files to a MediaWiki website.
For more information, see [[mw:Extension:MediaUploader]].

mediauploader-published:
Used as status message.

This message indicates it has been published successfully.
{{Identical|Published}}

mediauploader-next-file-despite-failures:
Used as label for the button.

Preceded by another button which is labeled {{msg-mw|mediauploader-file-retry}}.
{{Identical|Continue anyway}}

mediauploader-tooltip-skiptutorial:
The tooltip shown when clicking the checkbox in the first step, which enables the user to skip the introductory licensing tutorial in the future.

In right to left languages, use ←.

Parameters:
* $1 - the URL for the user preferences
* $2 - {{msg-mw|Prefs-uploads}}
* $3 - {{msg-mw|Prefs-mediauploader-interface}}

mediauploader-license-show-all:
Used as action link text.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|mediauploader-license-show-recommended}}

mediauploader-license-show-recommended:
Used as action link text.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|mediauploader-license-show-all}}

mediauploader-error-signature-too-long:
Used as error message. Parameters:
* $1 - maximum number of characters for the signature
{{Related|mediauploader-error-signature}}

mediauploader-error-signature-too-short:
Used as error message. Parameters:
* $1 - minimum number of characters for the signature
{{Related|mediauploader-error-signature}}

mediauploader-file-too-large-text:
Error message informing the user that their file is too large to upload. Parameters:
* $1 - the maximum file size
* $2 - the size of the file they tried to upload
These two parameters use any one of the following messages:
** {{msg-mw|Size-bytes}}
** {{msg-mw|Size-kilobytes}}
** {{msg-mw|Size-megabytes}}
** {{msg-mw|Size-gigabytes}}

mediauploader-categories-missing:
Used to let the user know that the category they entered does not have a description page, and thus is likely unused and not what they meant.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|visualeditor-dialog-meta-categories-missing}}

mediauploader-prefs-license-ownwork:
Parameters:
* $1 - license message. e.g. {{msg-mw|mediauploader-license-cc-by-sa-3.0}}
See also:
* {{msg-mw|mediauploader-prefs-license-thirdparty}}

mediauploader-prefs-license-thirdparty:
Parameters:
* $1 - license message. e.g. {{msg-mw|mediauploader-license-cc-by-sa-3.0}}
See also:
* {{msg-mw|mediauploader-prefs-license-own}}

